'''贝图拉·马哈苏德'''（{{lang-ur|بیت اللہ محسود}}，{{bd|1974年||2009年|8月5日|catIdx=M}}）<ref name="death_1">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8220762.stm|title=Taliban admit commander's death|date=25 August 2009|work=BBC|accessdate=25 August 2009|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827133409/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8220762.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/english/2009-08-06-voa54.cfm|title=Pakistan Foreign Minister: Taliban Chief Baitullah Mehsud is Dead|work=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]]|date=6 August 2009|author=Ayaz Gul|place=Islamabad|accessdate=7 August 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090807214628/http://www.voanews.com/english/2009-08-06-voa54.cfm|archivedate=2009-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSISL485349|title=Afghan Taliban say unhurt by Mehsud death|author=Hamid Shalizi|author2=Peter Graff|author3=Jeremy Laurence|work=Reuters|place=Kabul|date=7 August 2009|accessdate=7 August 2009|archive-date=2009-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810214833/http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSISL485349|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|塔利班运动]]创始人兼第1任领导人，2007年12月他把5个军事组织统合成巴基斯坦塔利班运动，他的麾下有5,000名武裝分子，他在巴基斯坦制造了多起爆炸和杀人事件<ref name=Tighe-Katz>{{cite news|author=Tighe, Paul and Katz, Ian|title=Pakistan Challenges Taliban to Show Leader Mehsud Still Alive |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087&sid=akFq_Knl5Gd0|work=Bloomberg|date=10 August 2009|accessdate=9 August 2009}}</ref><ref name="NYT22608">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/26/world/asia/26pstan.html|title=Blast Kills Surgeon General of Pakistani Army|publisher=New York Times|author=Masood, Salman|date=26 February 2008|accessdate=26 August 2008|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080227090258/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/26/world/asia/26pstan.html|archivedate=2008-02-27|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=abbash>Abbas, Hassan."[http://belfercenter.ksg.harvard.edu/publication/17868/profile_of_tehrikitaliban_pakistan.html A Profile of Tehrik-i-Taliban Pakistan] {{Wayback|url=http://belfercenter.ksg.harvard.edu/publication/17868/profile_of_tehrikitaliban_pakistan.html |date=20151001123326 }}". ''[[CTC_Sentinel|CTC Sentinel]]'' 1 (2): 1–4. January 2008.</ref>。

2009年8月5日贝图拉被美国[[无人侦察机|无人侦察机]]用[[炸弹|炸弹]]炸死<ref name=ap20090807>{{cite news|title=Aide says Pakistani Taliban leader Mehsud is dead|agency=Associated Press|date=7 August 2009|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090807/ap_on_re_as/as_pakistan|accessdate=7 August 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090810184923/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090807/ap_on_re_as/as_pakistan|archivedate=2009-08-10}}</ref>。起初[[哈基穆拉·马哈苏德|哈基穆拉·马哈苏德]]对外宣布贝图拉处于健康状态<ref name=AlJazeera-200908>{{cite news|title=Pakistan Taliban denies leader dead|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2009/08/2009887522640311.html|publisher=Aljazeera|date=8 August 2009|accessdate=7 August 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090808100657/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2009/08/2009887522640311.html|archivedate=2009-08-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>，但是巴基斯坦的{{link-en|阿塔尔·阿巴斯|Athar Abbas}}少將和[[美国白宫|美国白宫]]发言人[[罗伯特·吉布斯|罗伯特·吉布斯]]都宣布贝图拉已经丧生<ref>{{cite news|title=ISPR denies reports of Mehsud killing|url=http://story.malaysiasun.com/index.php/ct/9/cid/303b19022816233b/id/528137/cs/1/|publisher=Midwest Radio Network|work=Malayasia Sun|date=7 August 2009|accessdate=7 August 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090918163545/http://story.malaysiasun.com/index.php/ct/9/cid/303b19022816233b/id/528137/cs/1/|archivedate=2009-09-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=White House declines to confirm death of Taliban chief in Pakistan|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-08/08/content_11844782.htm|work=Xinhua|date=8 August 2009|accessdate=7 August 2009|archive-date=2012-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102174302/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-08/08/content_11844782.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年8月23日哈基穆拉·马哈苏德打电话给[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC），说贝图拉在8月23日死亡，原因是8月5日的美国无人侦察机的[[空袭|空袭]]<ref name=Subler>{{cite news|author=Subler, Jason, Graham, Patrick and Haider, Kamran|title=UPDATE 3-US says evidence Taliban chief dead "pretty conclusive"|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idINISL18195020090809|publisher=Thompson Reuters|work=Reuters|date=9 August 2009|accessdate=9 August 2009|archive-date=2009-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090919084935/http://in.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idINISL18195020090809|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年9月30日英国广播公司收到一份展示贝图拉身体的视频<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8282174.stm|work=BBC|title=Taliban film shows leader is dead|date=30 September 2009|accessdate=26 April 2010|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214111146/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8282174.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
